>



  <p>We process customer samples through our Alfa Laval Lab Scale Disc Centrifuge (manual clean type) to determine the applicability of centrifugation as a possible separation method. Lab-scale centrifuge sample testing lets Dolphin Centrifuge get a thorough understanding of your separation application and limitations if any.</p>

  <p>The test results allow us to recommend the right industrial centrifuge which will work for your process. Our explosion-proof, lab-scale disc centrifuge performs 3-phase separation and 2-phase clarification.</p>

  <p>Based on this testing, Dolphin Centrifuge can make an informed recommendation as to:<br>
  <strong>(a)</strong> Applicability &amp; limitations (if any) of an industrial centrifuge.<br>
  <strong>(b)</strong> Type and centrifuge model best suited for customer's needs.</p>

  <p>The customer benefits by being able to evaluate centrifuge performance on their product. The customer may also run further laboratory analysis on the returned samples to verify separation efficiency.</p>

