      allowfullscreen
      loading="lazy"
      class="rounded-lg shadow-md w-full max-w-xl aspect-video"
    ></iframe>
  </div>

  <h2 id="batch-testing">Small Batch Customer Sample Testing</h2>
  <p><a href="/">Dolphin Centrifuge</a> does have the in-house capability to batch process a sample (up to <strong>10 Gallons</strong>) through a small industrial-scale disc-stack centrifuge. Please call one of our centrifuge experts for details on this batch testing service.</p>

